snippet.title: Mission Zero | New Map Trailer：The Museum of Civilization
snippet.description:
The new map Museum of Civilization is divided into four areas: the prehistoric "Dino Pavilion,” the "Gallery" representing intelligent civilization, the "Culture Zone", and the "Planetarium" exhibition of the vast universe. 

- Pre-register now: https://www.missionzero.game/
- Discord: https://discord.gg/tQZTBYwgRC
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Missionzerogame
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/missionzero_EN
